description:
This is a 7 minute workout called 'Deep Relaxation in 7 Minutes (Guided Meditation) “The Circle of Wisdom”' from the channel The Honest Guys - Meditations - Relaxation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Sleep Prep vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: A short guided meditation that will induce deep relaxation as it conveys you to a mysterious land within a circle of wisdom stones, under the star-filled night sky.  This deep relaxation guided mediation will allow you to communicate with the universe and receive wisdom, leaving you deeply relaxed and at peace. 

This track is a remaster of the original track from our "GATEWAYS TO SERENITY" album; a unique collection of 13 short, fantasy guided meditations, designed to quickly calm your mind and bring you into a deep state of relaxation within the shortest possible time. 

The GATEWAYS TO SERENITY MP3 album is here:  https://www.thehonestguys.co.uk/digital-downloads/gts1-mp3

____________________________________

We are The Honest Guys and since 2009 we have been providing very high-quality guided sleep meditations, mindfulness meditations, and sleep music for anyone who needs it.
